<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.2">
<l>āvikāp pāriṉiyā rāḻkaṭaṉmaṇ viṇmūṭi</l>
<l>māvikāra māyōr valliravāy nīṇṭatāṟ</l>
<l>kāvicēr vaṇṇaṉeṉ kaṇṇaṉum vārāṉāl</l>
<l>pāviyē ṉeñcamē nīyumpāṅ kallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who will guard [my] soul now? Shrouding deep sea, earth [and] sky,</l>
<l>as a great change, as one harsh night [time] grows long.</l>
<l>He of Nelumbo colour, my Kaṇṇaṉ will not come,</l>
<l>o heart of me evil-doer, and you are without companion.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
